---
title: Sepolia Transaction Flow
---
flowchart TB
    User([Voter / Developer])
    Wallet[MetaMask Wallet]
    TX[Transaction<br/>castVote or register]
    
    subgraph Sepolia_Nodes[Sepolia Network Nodes]
        Node1[Node A<br/>Relay and Validate]
        Node2[Node B<br/>Relay and Validate]
        Node3[Node C<br/>Relay and Validate]
    end
    
    subgraph Validators["Permissioned Validator Set"]
        Proposer[Proposer<br/>Creates Block 1001]
        Attesters[Attesters<br/>Verify and Attest]
    end
    
    Block[New Block Added<br/>to Blockchain]
    BC[Sepolia Blockchain]
    Explorer[Sepolia Etherscan<br/>Blockchain Explorer]
    
    User -->|1. Connect| Wallet
    Wallet -->|2. Submit TX| TX
    TX -->|3. Broadcast| Sepolia_Nodes
    Sepolia_Nodes -->|4. Gossip and Validate| Proposer
    Proposer -->|5. Create Block| Block
    Attesters -->|6. Verify and Attest| Block
    Block -->|7. Add to Chain| BC
    BC -->|8. Index and Display| Explorer
    Explorer -->|9. View TX and Balance| User
    
    style Proposer fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style Attesters fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style Block fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
    style Explorer fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style BC fill:#607D8B,color:#fff
